title: Young Thug Feat. Quavo, Offset, Young Scooter "Guwop" Video
text:
Posted by Devon Jefferson , Jan 19, 2017 at 08:53pm Subscribe to HNHH TV Young Thug delivers a star-studded visual for "Guwop." 
Coming off of the release of his groundbreaking and unique video for "Wyclef Jean" Young Thug is back with visuals for the JEFFERY cut "Guwop." The flick is packed with stars as all three members of the Migos make cameos, in addition to Trey Songz , Desiigner and Meek Mill . 
The video is very chill as we see Thug, Quavo, Offset and Scooter dance around while rapping their verses and bare witness to one of the biggest high profile dice games to date. Additionally, the video features footage from Thug in concert and a dude dressed up in a Jason mask smoking a blunt. 
Check out the new JEFFERY visuals now and keep those eyes peeled for more from Young Thug in the days and weeks to come. Young Thug delivers a star-studded visual for "Guwop."
